Invocation Name: stuttgart guide
des:
Use the Stuttgart Guide Alexa skill to find interesting attractions and things to do in Stuttgart, Germany. Simply enable the skill and say "Alexa, open Stuttgart Guide" to begin. Or say "Alexa, ask Stuttgart Guide..."
• Alexa, tell me some facts about Stuttgart.
• Where should I go?
• Tell me the top five things.
This is a beta version. Stay tuned, more to come!
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
